description: 28×28 matrix indicating shared currencies and relationship types between all currency pairs

relationship_types_explained.base_base: Share base currency (e.g., EURUSD & EURGBP share EUR)
relationship_types_explained.quote_quote: Share quote currency (e.g., EURUSD & GBPUSD share USD)
relationship_types_explained.base_quote_cross: Pair1 base = Pair2 quote (e.g., EUR in EURUSD & GBPEUR)
relationship_types_explained.quote_base_cross: Pair1 quote = Pair2 base (e.g., USD in EURUSD & USDCAD)
